  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0b9f\u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Trying to sell the northern part of Sri Lanka to India?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mannar District Fishermen's Association President Mohammad Alam has said that he will sell the northern part to the Indian government in the current economic crisis.",
        "The political instability in the country today, fuel shortages as well as the wind power project to be set up in the Mannar district, the wind power project taken up by the Adani Group and other issues, as well as the problems faced by the people at the time are many.",
        "Last Thursday, an Indian delegation visited the Mannar district to discuss the Adani Group's plans.",
        "But at present the Sri Lankan government does not know how to use the resources available in Sri Lanka properly.",
        "The country has been pushed below the poverty line due to the lack of timely decisions for the future.",
        "Adani is one of the richest businessmen in India. There are a lot of problems for him. They are going to bring him in and sell the North. Of course, he said he was going to sell the North to India by implementing plans to develop the North in the current situation. (R)"
      ],
